data.description: GIANT and stunning home that sprawls almost 3000 SF of living space!    As you step inside, you are greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere! The interior of this house is a testament to tasteful design and quality craftsmanship. The designer paint and flooring create a seamless flow and add a touch of sophistication to every room. One of the standout features of this home is the VAULTED textured CEILINGS with RECESSED LIGHTING, which not only add a sense of grandeur but also provide ample illumination throughout the living spaces. The combination of the vaulted ceilings and the recessed lighting creates a visually stunning effect, enhancing the overall ambiance of the home. The bathrooms in this home have been remodeled & upgraded. The use of travertine, quartz, and slate materials exudes luxury and elegance. The designer cabinetry, mirrors, hardware, and sinks further elevate the aesthetic appeal of these spaces. Every detail has been carefully considered to create a spa-like atmosphere where you can relax and rejuvenate.  Prepare to be amazed by the GOURMET KITCHEN, which is truly a chef's dream. The dramatic designer touches, such as the elegant custom TREY CEILING with recessed lighting, make a bold statement. The kitchen features all-newer  designer cabinetry, hardware, sink, and appliances, ensuring both functionality and style. The QUARTZ COUNTERTOP with a SLATE and GLASS TILE BACKSPLASH add a modern and sleek touch to the space, creating a visually striking FOCAL POINT. Throughout the home, you will find wonderful interior plantation shutters, dual pane windows with architectural moldings, and new exterior fencing. These features not only enhance the aesthetic appeal of the home but also contribute to energy efficiency and privacy. The pride of ownership is evident in every aspect of this ''Haverford'' home, which is highly sought-after in this wonderful neighborhood. From the thoughtfully chosen upgrades to the impeccable attention to detail, this home truly stands out as a beautiful and highly upgraded residence. To truly appreciate its splendor, it must be seen in person.  Did I mention a NEW  whole house ATTIC FAN, NEW one-year ROOF, AC UNIT, WATER HEATER, GARAGE DOOR OPENER, and craftsman looking CABINETS in the garage.  The VACUUM System can be available if a new unit is installed. This home has lots of storage spaces,  and much more!!! ATTENTION VETERANS THIS IS WHAT YOU HAVE BEEN LOOKING FOR!!! YOU MAY ASSUME THIS LOW VA FIXED RATE AT ITS BEST!
